CBRE, as the exclusively appointed agents, is pleased to offer 185-187 Osborne Avenue, Clayton, for lease.

The property provides 4 x 10 tonne cranes and additional provisions for more to be installed. The property's location provides easy access to Princes Highway to the north and the Dingley Bypass to the south, linking the Melbourne CBD and the south eastern industrial precincts.

Property details:
+ Total building area: 4,214sqm*
+ Large land area of 9,300sqm*
+ 9 external motorised roller shutter doors 
+ Internal clearance of up to 9.6m*
+ 400amp* power supply with the ability to upgrade further
+ Industrial 1 Zone
+ Full drive around access
+ 4x 10 tonne cranes
+ Substantial hard stand at front and rear
+ Ample onsite carparking
+ Washdown bay available 

Location details:
+ M1 Monash Freeway 4.6km*
+ M3 Eastlink 6.3km*
+ Dingley Bypass 2.7km*

*approx.

Property Description:

- Located moments from the Princes Hwy in close proximity to the Monash Freeway
- Freestanding secure office/warehouse in tightly held pocket
- Ideal for a wide variety of uses including importers/exporters, wholesalers, transport & logistics, manufacturers

10% RETURN AVAILABLE!!
 3 YEAR LEASE
 Income:  $125,000 net per annum

 Industrial 1 Zone
 Clayton Homemaker Centre  nearby neighbours include Retravision, Barbeques Galore, Swan Plumbing

This unit is in a tightly held pocket of Clayton, conveniently located just off Centre Road, only moments from Westall Road and Princes Highway. Boasting fantastic truck and container access and great internal height, this unit would suit importer/exporters and small businesses.

Total building area: 420sqm*
Corporate style office: 60sqm*
High clearance warehouse: 360sqm*

Key features:

- Container height roller door

- Secure facility with electric gates
- Good truck access

*denotes approx.

CBRE is proud to exclusively offer 1858 Princes Highway, Clayton.  For Sale by way of Public Auction on Wednesday 25th September at 10:30am On Site.

This exciting opportunity is situated in the tightly held Monash precinct with unrivalled exposure to Princes Highway.


Property highlights include:

 Total floor area 795sqm*

 Showroom/warehouse 655sqm*

 Office 140sqm*

 6 car parks on title

 Newly refurbished

 Property faces the M-City residential and retail development which comprises three residential towers, 643 apartments, over 60 retail stores, office building and a 250 room Mantra Hotel

 Retail neighbours include: Rec Xpress a boutique gym, Michelins only high performance vehicle concept store in Australia, and Ishkas largest retail site and head office

 The property is situated 800m* from the Springvale Home Makers Centre  one of the largest homemaker centres in Australia

 Located 300m* from the Blackburn Road intersection, the property  experiences passing traffic of an estimated 60,000 vehicles* per day.

 The position allows for easy access to surrounding arterials including the Monash Freeway (3.3km*), Westall Bypass (800m*) and East Link is accessible via Monash Freeway or Princes Highway

 Public transport is in close proximity with buses running along Princes Hwy and Blackburn Road, which links to Clayton train station (2.5km*).

 Flexible Industrial 1 Zoning

To arrange an inspection or to obtain a copy of the information memorandum and legal documentation, please contact Bryce Pane, Sandra Ng or Chao Zhang.

*approx.

For this first time offered to the market in over 35 years, CBRE is pleased to offer 175 Wellington Road, Clayton for sale via Expressions of Interest closing Wednesday 10th March 2021 at 3pm AEST.

The site is located in the heart of the Monash employment cluster where we have seen significant commercial and industrial development.

This rare standalone facility has over 134m* frontage to Wellington Road, and has easy access to the Monash Freeway and Eastlink and is well serviced by Springvale and Blackburn Roads. 

The site itself has flexible Special use zoning (SUZ6) allowing both commercial and industrial development in the future (STCA).

-	Total building area: 4,026sqm*
-	Land Area: 10,390sqm*
-	Low site coverage site
-	Over 134m* exposure to Wellington Road
-	Two level office and amenities
-	High clearance warehouse with 7 Roller shutter doors
-	Huge power capacity of 2,500KvA*
-	Large rear hardstand or expansion area (STCA)
-	Easy access to Monash Freeway and Eastlink
-	Surrounded by major occupiers including Mazda, Nissan, Pfizer, Mercedes Benz and BMW
-	Expose your business to a large amount of vehicles per day

For sale by Expressions of Interest closing Wednesday 10th March 2021 at 3pm AEST.
